Title: Android - Fix SDK Dependency Conflicts for Orange Integration
Description: As an integrating mobile developer I want the eNROLL SDK to be compatible with Orange application dependency versions so that the SDK does not crash at runtime. ROOT CAUSE: Gradle dependency resolution selected Orange higher versions at runtime causing NoSuchMethodError crashes. SOLUTION: Upgraded SDK to Kotlin 1.9.25 and Lottie 6.6.2 and Material3 1.3.1 and Compose UI 1.7.4. PUBLISHED: SDK v1.5.10 on JitPack
Acceptance Criteria: 1. SDK works without crashes 2. No NoSuchMethodError when launching SDK 3. All existing SDK functionality works 4. New version published to JitPack 5. Backward compatibility maintained

Title: Upgrade SDK Dependencies
Description: Updated SDK dependencies to match Orange versions
